org.forgerock.opendj.server.config.client

Interface NumSubordinatesVirtualAttributeCfgClient

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ConfigurationClient, VirtualAttributeCfgClient

    public interface NumSubordinatesVirtualAttributeCfgClient
extends VirtualAttributeCfgClient
    A client-side interface for reading and modifying Num Subordinates Virtual Attribute settings.

    The Num Subordinates Virtual Attribute generates a virtual attribute that specifies the number of immediate child entries that exist below the entry.
